latestIgtvVideos.title: Welcome to the teenage years! Adaa ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
You don’t need a long guest list or a pile of presents.  A perfect plan can make your child’s big day the best of the year.

When my daughter turned 13 last week, we threw a small get together @unlocked.in

Amazing food, cool board games and a escape room that make this place perfect.

Escape room 🕵️‍♂
The kids seemed to love the concept and were engaged completely in the activity.
Engaging and a challenging puzzle. Hints were crisp and ensured a right balance of help and suspense. The room was well designed and clues well placed. The overall experience was super fun and interesting. 

Keeping things simple and ringing in the milestone with her besties was the perfect plan to celebrate my teenager's special day. 

Here is evidence of these brave souls who have survived the escape room ‘Lionheart’s Mystery’.

I cannot begin to find the words to say thank you for your hospitality @satya.ikandy . GM Satya really took great care of all of us. 

@unlocked.in Bar and Kitchen is a space that makes space for leisure time, great good and an ambience that will soothe you.

Highly Recommend ❤️

For all die-hard fans of Thai food – Baan Thai is love!  Food ... deliciously rich tickled up our tastebuds and the friendly greetings from their staff made our day.

“Aromas of Baan Thai”

I cannot wait to return to this little gem.

latestPosts.caption:
A slice of Mexico in Gurgaon—and I’m OBSESSED! 🇲🇽🌮✨ @missmargaritabyarriba 

Dropped by the newly opened Miss Margarita at Global Gateway Towers, and trust me—you’re going to want to bookmark this spot ASAP. From vibrant interiors to the zingy cocktails (hello, tequila bar 👀🍹), it’s giving full-on vacay vibes right here in the city!

Their summer menu is all kinds of fire 🔥—think crispy tacos, loaded nachos, juicy grilled corn, and the most refreshing watermelon salad I’ve had in a while. Every bite = sunshine and spice in perfect balance ☀️🌶️

If you love bold flavours, chilled margaritas, and a space that’s buzzing with energy—Miss Margarita is where you need to be this weekend. Come hungry and leave with a happy heart (and maybe a slight tequila buzz 😋).

#MissMargaritaGurgaon #MexicanCravings #GurgaonEats #InfluencerDiaries #tacotuesdayeveryday
